      "side": 1,
      "message": "I thought the vision here was that bicubic would become a shader combinator,  shader\u0027 \u003d bicubic(shader, params...), and that no file in Skia would contain the words \"image\" and \"bicubic\".  We should be able to bicubic sample a gradient just as well as an image?  (For that matter, bilerp is another good shader combinator that just happens to have better native support in images...)",
